  <!-- EN: A subterranean bastion cloaked in neutron-charged plating, impervious to directed energy weapons including plasma cannons. When health drops below 25% or it is one holdfire mode, it descends for repairs - consuming 50 steel and quadruple power every 10 seconds to restore 100 HP. Though its suppressive fire lacks precision, the tortoise-shell armor renders it nigh indestructible against frontal assaults. -->
  <CMC_ReinforcedBunker_Fire.description>安装有重型装甲的喷火器碉堡，当生命值低于25%或手动停火时，碉堡会降入地下维修，每10秒消耗50钢铁和4倍电力，修复100点生命值。</CMC_ReinforcedBunker_Fire.description>
